      <name>Missing Males</name>
<Placemark>
        <name>Lester McAllister, 1918</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwPNsEYiifB_NLztyGoMW1rm6M2XTPqA6lCnNhBfj_38E3j_fVbwKUriV7dgsdfCDMkeBruj_ZNIT-RNYhCHPOQ2Q5kz0EpInwCjg0IJxAFLSFo7sOW0ifdPcqD_QP3MW43jbGedVJR1iE6voBCxSgv847UyCQPQVdZFYmqrkfSxaglSC8Vgft4UEn6Ix5LT9gwMO3UtIvhkBv4uXH09thiZ8Jub7arSKIqlnJoSWz7lO6yN4I1JwtmgpZ7Zg?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Last seen on July 4, 1918, in Liberty Park, Salt Lake City. 6-year-old Lester had attended the Independence Day celebrations with his older brother and a group of neighborhood children. His brother left him with another companion, but when he returned, Lester was gone. <br>Another 6-year-old told a story that Lester may have slipped and drowned in one of the ponds in the park but later said he did not know what happened. The ponds were all drained and dragged several times without success. <br>The possibility of abduction was also raised. <br>Several witnesses came forward to say they saw Lester after leaving Liberty Park and looking for his way home.<br>Lester was slightly small for his age. He also had a stroke of paralysis that left him with limited use of his left leg and considerably affected his speech. He had a light complexion. He was dressed in kickerbockers and a soilder's hat.<br><br>No Case #, No Links<br><br>Please contact the Utah State Cold Case Tip Hotline: 833-DPS-SAFE (833-377-7233)<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwQplkelmX0AV3KndRpVinBdmL3d2a07J4wdM_rmOk4EoknFbS9QR8x7-ZWuCP0RQxuQKe35dXrbl9EKQ2u2HE5VAIWiSd08Cw9J4bbgVtPp1n9eCkLgm4BkXuQyNT0Fi3pgijjVfJlMNLjNejP_jz42WukrGAek2JhVhJ0YRuQP91yg6mOCah5pk9pyzj8xL3MRFetmBPDFd2qnD-OJj2OYUuVJ07FYHE5zkh6M9kXMqMy9A1fNcm0yAN2uQ?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwPNsEYiifB_NLztyGoMW1rm6M2XTPqA6lCnNhBfj_38E3j_fVbwKUriV7dgsdfCDMkeBruj_ZNIT-RNYhCHPOQ2Q5kz0EpInwCjg0IJxAFLSFo7sOW0ifdPcqD_QP3MW43jbGedVJR1iE6voBCxSgv847UyCQPQVdZFYmqrkfSxaglSC8Vgft4UEn6Ix5LT9gwMO3UtIvhkBv4uXH09thiZ8Jub7arSKIqlnJoSWz7lO6yN4I1JwtmgpZ7Zg?fife=s16383 https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwQplkelmX0AV3KndRpVinBdmL3d2a07J4wdM_rmOk4EoknFbS9QR8x7-ZWuCP0RQxuQKe35dXrbl9EKQ2u2HE5VAIWiSd08Cw9J4bbgVtPp1n9eCkLgm4BkXuQyNT0Fi3pgijjVfJlMNLjNejP_jz42WukrGAek2JhVhJ0YRuQP91yg6mOCah5pk9pyzj8xL3MRFetmBPDFd2qnD-OJj2OYUuVJ07FYHE5zkh6M9kXMqMy9A1fNcm0yAN2uQ?fife=s16383</value>
