<Placemark>
        <name>Everett Ruess, 1934</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GxdSI-4tCZPhwzt9Yt6Ygq0AJdXRo6EAoRqxFYH9mLGKu5t8sYf0fdxZoWntnELp012xG-tC9b03_BOR_RKQnMY0FS_lRz_NmphFLQGW3a93W6Z3QLHWVx8QyLIhvhq65WN33UZK-8Kkhdj2NQo43qBH1Jtk65GMvmC1Je2RdzY4h5RliZZm5OqmpoyZyxHEG5UICX84TpBedTQwMGkqac-QIE0FkWGKTXttcGnh8Slw-MheCwik1vsvG6K4w?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Last seen November 1934, in Escalante, heading out to the nearby canyons on his way to Arizona. A corral he had made at his campsite and his two burros were found near the north side of Davis Gulch, a canyon of the Escalante River.<br><br>Garfield County Sheriff's Office Case #0042753<br>https://bci.utah.gov/coldcases/everett-ruess/<br>DoeNetwork: https://www.doenetwork.org/cases/4435dmut.html<br>Namus: https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/53417<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GxMhiwb4kcN4KzEYp8dAnXA22IvY4jo59G5Ri2nGTa7sGXrYk3BJMCjnvuJkCwmp3XcZrRYda814uTQ44s5-Tt-Wvy_xaXFUyRa4pTV9sxqonzEdwBptwhV_qI9jdhDvYWW5w-4_nu77zc1BfsZCC_DiVPFECxYq3geDkexfq7iE2lG9JcyXsOdzyiJxEHdjixw2WQNDqXHxf4zVzzVWu9dTJi2M3JEPLRFMB8-W-HqhrqT7B9fx81EzqDxDQ?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwzICvMSo55LRAUwsnhlySIVgMwEHymquUNtrTTi28BkIs8eWo-7PB6A6ZYZhi196xobkAcHGZsP6YbFZSojaLp11cLMBPYNhikxOpmKRI6_Kybm0Dgp8wQw7BVjL0tCcKM7fds5iBQbzEB6xPUt1ue3ZcCSf8EoJnL5NMKweWsjRiT8fHHFI2IdymgZN7rttI724F9uGQ0T34N-Ifm-dPxi6qt9syZAIO7_G8-nP4ZkASfobZm6BMLYWVG5A?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwVjMbuI6Dt1dXHnu_Fkm2Dnf1jUYzt1biSzDhp2lIj-e-fEBB4vbz6423nTbTe2ZU8VhPMprf8Utj3DA0HnFaEcdMyQoHe_3Vt4xT90Y_Del9vgmNEoYLrtHo-C-fvcov6amN0pt9mu6nggHpFBwd77Q7E9g4cepO6HHQCoXWWFxpTulEXkzIOcY3EJs2Q70CPm-hhIgm_gDSaED-4wvMz8wxxZV99eJE8a4ZhQk1Va35d4yKrZdIlWSkRlg?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https